<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-1a' );" name="011-1a" class="pb">[011-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　周禮句解卷十一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:221'>　　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　朱申　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:259'>　　冬官考工記第六<span class='krp-note'>鄭氏曰古周禮六篇司空之官/也司空之篇亡漢興購千金不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='259:302'>　　　<span class='krp-note'>得後人錄此三十工以為考工記備大數耳名/今按冬官不名司空而名考工記者蓋漢儒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='302:312'>　　　<span class='krp-note'>之/也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='312:323'>　　　冬官考工記上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='323:364'>國有六職<span class='krp-note'>謂國家之事有此六種職掌如下文坐/而論道以下六條非謂小宰之六職也</span>百工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='364:390'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-1b' );" name="011-1b" class="pb">[011-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='390:427'>　與居一焉<span class='krp-note'>百工審曲面勢以飭五材以辨/民器居六職之一也與音預</span>或坐而論</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='427:470'>　道<span class='krp-note'>王與三公坐而論道/經邦此六職之一也</span>或作而行之<span class='krp-note'>作猶起也行猶/為也王公論之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='470:514'>　<span class='krp-note'>士大夫則起而有/為此六職之二也</span>或審曲面埶<span class='krp-note'>審察五材之曲直面/觀五材之形勢埶勢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='514:555'>　以飭五材<span class='krp-note'>飾猶修也五材/金木水火土也</span>以辨名器<span class='krp-note'>五材既修乃分/辨之以為民之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='555:594'>　<span class='krp-note'>器用此百工之/事六職之三也</span>或通四方之珍異以資之<span class='krp-note'>物貴為珍/物殊為異</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='594:636'>　<span class='krp-note'>通四方之有無而相資以為/用此商旅之事六職之四也</span>或飭力以長地財<span class='krp-note'>地財/九穀</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='636:678'>　<span class='krp-note'>也必勤力以長成之此/三農之事六職之五也</span>或治絲麻以成之<span class='krp-note'>治絲以成/帛治麻以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='678:719'>　<span class='krp-note'>成布此嬪婦之/事六職之六也</span>坐而論道謂之王公<span class='krp-note'>此覆解上文六/條謂坐而論道</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='719:745'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-2a' );" name="011-2a" class="pb">[011-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='745:784'>　<span class='krp-note'>者王與三/公之職也</span>作而行之謂之士大夫<span class='krp-note'>謂作而行之者士/與大夫之職也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='784:814'>　審曲面勢以飭五材以辨民器謂之百工<span class='krp-note'>審察五材/曲直方面</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='814:848'>　<span class='krp-note'>形勢以為民器謂主/此事者百工之職也</span>通四方之珍異以資之謂之商</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='848:885'>　旅<span class='krp-note'>謂主此事者掌/商旅之職也</span>飭力以長地財謂之農夫<span class='krp-note'>謂主此/事者掌</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='885:920'>　<span class='krp-note'>農夫之/職也</span>治絲麻以成之謂之婦功<span class='krp-note'>謂主此事者掌/婦功之職也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='920:962'>　粤無鎛<span class='krp-note'>粤南蠻地也鎛治田器也言其/地無鑄鎛者之名粤曰鎛搏</span>燕無函<span class='krp-note'>燕北/狄地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='962:1008'>　<span class='krp-note'>也函甲也言其地/無函人之名函含</span>秦無廬<span class='krp-note'>秦西戎地也廬兵戈之柄/也言其地無廬人之名廬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='1008:1049'>　<span class='krp-note'>盧/</span>胡無弓車<span class='krp-note'>胡北夷地也言其地/無弓人車人之名</span>粤之無鎛也<span class='krp-note'>此覆/解上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='1049:1075'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-2b' );" name="011-2b" class="pb">[011-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1075:1112'>　<span class='krp-note'>文四條釋粤/無鎛之義</span>非無鎛也<span class='krp-note'>非是其地/無鎛手也</span>夫人而能為鎛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1112:1153'>　<span class='krp-note'>人人皆能為鎛故鎛工/不以名著也夫扶下同</span>燕之無函也<span class='krp-note'>釋燕無/函之義</span>非無函</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1153:1193'>　也<span class='krp-note'>非是其地/無函人也</span>夫人而能為函也<span class='krp-note'>人人皆能為甲故/函人不以名著也</span>秦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1193:1229'>　之無廬也<span class='krp-note'>釋秦無/廬之義</span>非無廬也<span class='krp-note'>非是其地/無廬人也</span>夫人而能為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1229:1268'>　廬也<span class='krp-note'>人人皆能為廬故/廬人不以名著也</span>胡之無弓車也<span class='krp-note'>釋胡無弓/車之義</span>非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1268:1305'>　無弓車也<span class='krp-note'>非是其地無/弓人車人也</span>夫人而能為弓車也<span class='krp-note'>人人皆/能為弓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1305:1349'>　<span class='krp-note'>與車故弓人車/人不以名著也</span>知者創物<span class='krp-note'>創謂立法於物也知者無/所不知故能創造器用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1349:1384'>　巧者述之<span class='krp-note'>述謂取法於後也巧者無/所不能故能倣傚為之</span>守之世謂之工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1384:1410'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-3a' );" name="011-3a" class="pb">[011-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1410:1453'>　<span class='krp-note'>父子相傳不失其/業然後名之曰工</span>百工之事<span class='krp-note'>百工不一其事皆/父子世守其業者</span>皆聖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1453:1489'>　人之作也<span class='krp-note'>聖人知無不知故百工之事/皆出於聖人創物之知也</span>爍金以為刄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1489:1533'>　<span class='krp-note'>金性至堅必待火以爍之/然後可以為刄爍始灼反</span>凝土以為器<span class='krp-note'>土性至緩必/待水以凝之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1533:1574'>　<span class='krp-note'>然後可以/為器也</span>作車以行陸<span class='krp-note'>行陸路者必/待車以載之</span>作舟以行水<span class='krp-note'>行/水</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1574:1615'>　<span class='krp-note'>道者必待/舟以載之</span>此皆聖人之所作也<span class='krp-note'>四者雖百工之事然/而知金之可爍土之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1615:1659'>　<span class='krp-note'>可凝車之可以行陸舟之可以行/水此皆出於聖人創物之知也</span>天有時<span class='krp-note'>天時有寒/温之殊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1659:1697'>　地有氣<span class='krp-note'>地氣有剛/柔之別</span>材有美<span class='krp-note'>均之為材料也而/有美惡之不同</span>工有巧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1697:1740'>　<span class='krp-note'>均之為工匠也而/有巧拙之或異</span>合此四者<span class='krp-note'>材既美工既巧又得/天時地氣四者相合</span>然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1740:1766'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-3b' );" name="011-3b" class="pb">[011-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1766:1804'>　後可以為良<span class='krp-note'>以此為器然/後極至於善</span>材美工巧<span class='krp-note'>材料雖美/工匠雖巧</span>然而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1804:1843'>　不良<span class='krp-note'>而所作之器/乃不善何也</span>則不時不得地氣也<span class='krp-note'>蓋由不得天/時地氣故不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1843:1885'>　<span class='krp-note'>良/也</span>橘踰淮而北為枳<span class='krp-note'>淮今淮河也橘味甘枳味苦以/江南之橘移過淮北則化為枳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1885:1929'>　<span class='krp-note'>枳/紙</span>鸜鵒不踰濟<span class='krp-note'>濟水在齊地鸜鵒之禽不過此水故/春秋書鸜鵒來巢以為異也鸜其俱</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1929:1969'>　<span class='krp-note'>鵒/欲</span>貉踰汶則死<span class='krp-note'>貉禽名似狐汶水在魯地/貉獸過此水則死貉戸各</span>此地氣然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1969:2013'>　也<span class='krp-note'>此地道之/化使然也</span>鄭之刀<span class='krp-note'>鄭國之地/其刀良</span>宋之斤<span class='krp-note'>斤斧類宋國/之地其斤良</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='2013:2052'>　魯之削<span class='krp-note'>削書刀也魯國/之地其削良</span>吳粤之劍<span class='krp-note'>吳粤二國之地/其劍良粤曰</span>遷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='2052:2089'>　乎其地而弗能為良<span class='krp-note'>雖使五國之人遷於他國之/地而制此器則不良者何也</span>地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='2089:2115'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-4a' );" name="011-4a" class="pb">[011-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='2115:2159'>　氣然也<span class='krp-note'>蓋由物性之宜使然也/  以上兩節言地有氣</span>燕之角<span class='krp-note'>燕地在北方/其牛角最堅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='2159:2203'>　<span class='krp-note'>實/</span>荆之幹<span class='krp-note'>荆地在南方多堅/木可為弓弩之幹</span>妢胡之笴<span class='krp-note'>妢胡胡子國/也近楚其地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='2203:2244'>　<span class='krp-note'>多幹可為箭幹/妢扶弓笴古老</span>吳粤之金錫<span class='krp-note'>吳粤在東南多/石山産金與錫</span>此材之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='2244:2286'>　美者也<span class='krp-note'>此材之稟天時地氣自然而/美者也  此一節言材有美</span>天有時以生<span class='krp-note'>陽/一</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='2286:2326'>　<span class='krp-note'>嘘而萬/物生</span>有時以殺<span class='krp-note'>隂一吸而/萬物殺</span>草木有時以生<span class='krp-note'>春夏陽/盛故草</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='2326:2369'>　<span class='krp-note'>木/生</span>有時以死<span class='krp-note'>秋冬隂盛/故草木死</span>石有時以泐<span class='krp-note'>石雖至堅或以/盛暑而解散也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='2369:2412'>　<span class='krp-note'>泐/勒</span>水有時以凝<span class='krp-note'>水雖流動或以/盛寒而凍結也</span>有時以澤<span class='krp-note'>水雖凍結/又以春時</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2412:2453'>　<span class='krp-note'>而消澤/也澤亦</span>此天時也<span class='krp-note'>此物之係乎天者然也/  此一節言天有時</span>凡攻木之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2453:2479'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-4b' );" name="011-4b" class="pb">[011-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2479:2520'>　工七<span class='krp-note'>自此而下言工有巧攻治/也治木之工其目有七</span>攻金之工六<span class='krp-note'>治金之/工其目</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2520:2561'>　<span class='krp-note'>有/六</span>攻皮之工五<span class='krp-note'>治皮革之工/其目有五</span>設色之工五<span class='krp-note'>裝設采色/之工其目</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2561:2601'>　<span class='krp-note'>有/五</span>刮摩之工五<span class='krp-note'>刮以成質磨以出細為此/工者其目有五刮古八反</span>搏埴之工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2601:2645'>　二<span class='krp-note'>搏團也埴土粘也蓋為瓦器者其目/有二凡此六者總為三十工也摶團</span>攻木之工<span class='krp-note'>此/覆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2645:2698'>　<span class='krp-note'>解上文六條言攻木/之工七其目在下</span>輪<span class='krp-note'>為輪/為蓋</span>輿<span class='krp-note'>為/輿</span>弓<span class='krp-note'>為/弓</span>廬<span class='krp-note'>為廬器蓋/戈㦸殳矛</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2698:2757'>　<span class='krp-note'>之柄也/廬盧</span>匠<span class='krp-note'>建國為宫/室為溝洫</span>車<span class='krp-note'>為耒/為車</span>梓<span class='krp-note'>為筍<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1206' title='KR1206' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1206.png'/>為飲器為侯/  此七者攻木之工</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2757:2809'>　<span class='krp-note'>也/</span>攻金之工<span class='krp-note'>其目/在下</span>築<span class='krp-note'>為/削</span>治<span class='krp-note'>為戈/㦸</span>鳬<span class='krp-note'>為/鍾</span>㮚<span class='krp-note'>為量/㮚栗</span>段<span class='krp-note'>為/鎛</span>桃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2809:2859'>　<span class='krp-note'>為劍之此六者/攻金  工也</span>攻皮之工<span class='krp-note'>其目/在下</span>函<span class='krp-note'>為/甲</span>鮑<span class='krp-note'>治/皮</span>韗<span class='krp-note'>為皷/韗運</span>韋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2859:2885'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-5a' );" name="011-5a" class="pb">[011-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2885:2932'>　<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span>裘<span class='krp-note'>為裘之此五者/攻皮  工也</span>設色之工<span class='krp-note'>其目/在下</span>畫繢<span class='krp-note'>繢言其意/畫言其事</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2932:2980'>　<span class='krp-note'>二者相須也/畫胡卦繢㑹</span>鍾<span class='krp-note'>深/羽</span>筐<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span>㡛<span class='krp-note'>練絲工此五者設/色之  也㡛芒</span>刮摩之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2980:3030'>　工<span class='krp-note'>其目/在下</span>玉<span class='krp-note'>治圭/璧</span>楖雕<span class='krp-note'>闕楖/側筆</span>矢<span class='krp-note'>為/矢</span>磬<span class='krp-note'>為磬之此五者/刮摩  工也</span>搏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='3030:3072'>　埴之工<span class='krp-note'>其目/在下</span>陶<span class='krp-note'>為/瓦</span>旊<span class='krp-note'>為簋工此二者搏/埴之  也旊倣</span>有虞氏上陶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='3072:3116'>　<span class='krp-note'>上與尚同虞舜時淳朴/未散陶土為器故上陶</span>夏后氏上匠<span class='krp-note'>夏時營制稍興/為宫室以居處</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='3116:3159'>　<span class='krp-note'>為溝洫以灌/溉故上匠</span>殷人上梓<span class='krp-note'>商禮樂之器/漸備故上梓</span>周人上輿<span class='krp-note'>周則/經制</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='3159:3195'>　<span class='krp-note'>廣而庶事/備故上輿</span>故一器而工聚焉者車為多<span class='krp-note'>此因周人/上輿而言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='3195:3227'>　<span class='krp-note'>蓋車雖一器而用/衆工為最多也</span>車有六等之數車軫四尺謂之一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='3227:3253'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-5b' );" name="011-5b" class="pb">[011-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='3253:3276'>　等戈柲六尺有六寸既建而迆崇於軫四尺謂之二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='3276:3299'>　等人長八尺崇於戈四尺謂之三等殳長尋有四尺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='3299:3322'>　崇於人四尺謂之四等車㦸常崇於殳四尺謂之五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='3322:3345'>　等酋矛常有四尺崇於㦸四尺謂之六等車謂之六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='3345:3375'>　等之數凡察車之道<span class='krp-note'>大凡察車/高下之法</span>必自載於地者始也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='3375:3414'>　<span class='krp-note'>自從也載於/地者謂輪也</span>是故察車自輪始<span class='krp-note'>輪廣則車髙/輪狹則車卑</span>凡察車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='3414:3437'>　之道欲有樸屬而㣲至不其屬無以為完乆也不㣲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='3437:3460'>　至無以為戚速也輪已崇則人不能登也輪已卑則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='3460:3486'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-6a' );" name="011-6a" class="pb">[011-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='3486:3515'>　於馬終古登阤也故兵車之輪六尺有六寸<span class='krp-note'>兵車革/路也凡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='3515:3551'>　<span class='krp-note'>輪之尺寸皆量/其圓徑之數</span>田車之輪六尺有三寸<span class='krp-note'>田車木/路也</span>乗車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3551:3590'>　之輪六尺有六寸<span class='krp-note'>乗車玉路金路象路也輪之尺寸/不同者以所駕馬有高下也乘去</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3590:3623'>　<span class='krp-note'>聲/</span>六尺有六寸之輪<span class='krp-note'>輪之圓有/六尺六寸</span>軹崇三尺有三寸也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3623:3666'>　<span class='krp-note'>軹軸頭也崇髙也輪徑六尺六寸軸/頭處中故但髙三尺三寸也軹紙</span>加軫與轐焉<span class='krp-note'>輿/後</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3666:3708'>　<span class='krp-note'>横木謂之軫軸上伏兔謂之轐車軸上有轐/轐尾上載車軫軫上加輿共髙七寸轐卜</span>四尺也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3708:3751'>　<span class='krp-note'>三尺三寸又加/七寸故髙四尺</span>人長八尺<span class='krp-note'>人有長短取中而言/之故曰八尺長去聲</span>登下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3751:3781'>　以為節<span class='krp-note'>車之髙於人為半故登車下/車以此為節則得其宜也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3781:3807'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-6b' );" name="011-6b" class="pb">[011-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3807:3843'>輪人為輪斬三材必以其時<span class='krp-note'>三材所以為轂也輻也牙/也斬之以時者陽木則仲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3843:3887'>　<span class='krp-note'>冬斬之隂木/則仲夏斬之</span>三材既具<span class='krp-note'>三材既/已具備</span>巧者和之<span class='krp-note'>必資工之/巧者和合</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3887:3916'>　<span class='krp-note'>三材以/為輪也</span>轂也者以為利轉也輻也者以為直指也牙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3916:3939'>　也者以為固抱也輪敝三材不失職謂之完望而眡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3939:3962'>　其輪欲其幎爾而下迆也進而眡之欲其㣲至也無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3962:3985'>　所取之取諸圜也望其輻欲其揱爾而纎也進而眡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3985:4008'>　之欲其内稱也無所取之取諸易直也望其轂欲其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='4008:4031'>　眼也進而眡之欲其幬之廉也無所取之取諸急也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='4031:4057'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-7a' );" name="011-7a" class="pb">[011-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='4057:4080'>　眡其綆欲其蚤之正也察其菑蚤不齵則輪雖敝不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='4080:4114'>　匡　凡斬轂之道必矩其隂陽<span class='krp-note'>矩謂刻識之也凡斬/轂材必辨其向日背</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='4114:4151'>　<span class='krp-note'>日之隂/陽方</span>陽也者稹理而堅<span class='krp-note'>陽木實栗叢緻也/謂稹理而堅實</span>隂也者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='4151:4184'>　疏理而柔<span class='krp-note'>隂木其體虚空故/疏而不宻其質弱</span>是故以火養其隂而齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='4184:4221'>　諸其陽<span class='krp-note'>必以火而/煉治之</span>則轂雖敝不藃<span class='krp-note'>雖乆而敝亦/不壞藃音耗</span>轂小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='4221:4256'>　而長則柞<span class='krp-note'>柞謂狹/而不廣</span>大而短則摯<span class='krp-note'>摯危也言/不堅固</span>是故六分</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='4256:4279'>　其輪崇以其一為之牙圍參分其牙圍而漆其二椁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='4279:4302'>　其漆内而中詘之以為之轂長以其長為之圍以其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='4302:4328'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-7b' );" name="011-7b" class="pb">[011-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='4328:4351'>　圍之阞捎其藪五分其轂之長去一以為賢去三以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='4351:4389'>　為軹　容轂必直<span class='krp-note'>非和轉之勢/故欲其直</span>陳篆必正<span class='krp-note'>采以約之/為篆文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='4389:4426'>　施膠必厚<span class='krp-note'>附麗之必/欲固也</span>施筋必數<span class='krp-note'>幔角之用必/欲多也數朔</span>幬必負</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='4426:4461'>　榦<span class='krp-note'>幬覆也幬以幔轂必欲/其廉之外見而負於榦</span>既摩革色青白謂之轂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='4461:4484'>　善參分其轂長二在外一在内以置其輻凡輻量其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='4484:4507'>　鑿深以為輻廣輻廣而鑿淺則是以大扤雖有良工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='4507:4530'>　莫之能固鑿深而輻小則是固有餘而强不足也故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='4530:4553'>　竑其輻廣以為之弱則雖有重任轂不折參分其輻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='4553:4579'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-8a' );" name="011-8a" class="pb">[011-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4579:4602'>　之長而殺其一則雖有深泥亦弗之溓也參分其股</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4602:4632'>　圍去一為骰圍　揉輻必齊<span class='krp-note'>揉輻以火所/以齊曲直</span>平沈必均</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4632:4673'>　<span class='krp-note'>沈輻以水所/以均輕重</span>直以指牙<span class='krp-note'>然輻直則為倨牙曲則/為勾故必欲其直指</span>牙得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4673:4699'>　則無𣙗而固不得則有𣙗必足見也六尺有六寸之輪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4699:4727'>　綆參分寸之二謂之輪之固　凡為輪<span class='krp-note'>為輪/之法</span>行澤者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4727:4768'>　欲杼<span class='krp-note'>澤多濕故削其輪之外/如劍脊也杼直吕反</span>行山者欲侔<span class='krp-note'>山多石故/輪欲上下</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4768:4809'>　<span class='krp-note'>相等而/圓滑也</span>杼以行澤<span class='krp-note'>以輪之杼/者而行澤</span>則是刀以割塗也<span class='krp-note'>譬如/以刀</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='4809:4851'>　<span class='krp-note'>而割/泥也</span>是故塗不附<span class='krp-note'>故雖行濕地而/泥不附者也</span>侔以行山<span class='krp-note'>以輪之/侔者而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='4851:4877'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-8b' );" name="011-8b" class="pb">[011-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='4877:4914'>　<span class='krp-note'>行/山</span>則是搏以行石也<span class='krp-note'>譬如以圓滑之物/而行石也搏音圓</span>是故輪雖敝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='4914:4950'>　不甐於鑿<span class='krp-note'>輪雖為石損敝而不動於/鑿中也甐力刄鑿曹報反</span>凡揉牙外不廉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='4950:4973'>　而内不挫旁不腫謂之用火之善是故規之以眡其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='4973:5013'>　圜也<span class='krp-note'>輪中規/則圜矣</span>萭之以眡其匡也<span class='krp-note'>萭與矩同規圜中矩/四圍端正是中矩也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='5013:5046'>　縣之以眡其輻之直也<span class='krp-note'>以繩縣之中繩/則輻直矣縣𤣥</span>水之以眡其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='5046:5080'>　平沈之均也<span class='krp-note'>偃其輪而灌以水其平/沈適均則平中準矣</span>量其藪以黍以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='5080:5118'>　眡其同也<span class='krp-note'>藪輻間也量之以黍而所受多/寡適同焉則中量矣藪素口反</span>權之以眡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='5118:5154'>　其輕重之侔也<span class='krp-note'>權稱鍾也以兩輪分而稱/之其輕重適侔則中權矣</span>故可規可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='5154:5180'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-9a' );" name="011-9a" class="pb">[011-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='5180:5212'>　萭可水可縣可量可權也<span class='krp-note'>六者皆曰可者/見其無不善也</span>謂之國工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='5212:5227'>　<span class='krp-note'>則國人無以/過其巧矣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='5227:5268'>輪人為蓋<span class='krp-note'>蓋取其圓於/車上之所用</span>達常圍三寸<span class='krp-note'>蓋之為制上為部/中為達常柄通上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='5268:5307'>　<span class='krp-note'>下/也</span>桯圍倍之六寸<span class='krp-note'>下為桯蓋扛也蓋之材/賴之以呈蓋頂也桯楹</span>信其桯圍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='5307:5342'>　以為部廣<span class='krp-note'>廣徑也部廣之圍尺有/八寸信音申廣古曠反</span>部廣六寸部長二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='5342:5365'>　尺桯長部之四尺者二十分寸之一謂之枚部尊一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='5365:5388'>　枚弓鑿廣四枚鑿上二枚鑿下四枚鑿深二寸有半</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='5388:5411'>　下直二故鑿端一枚弓長六尺謂之庇軹五尺謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='5411:5437'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-9b' );" name="011-9b" class="pb">[011-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='5437:5460'>　庇輪四尺謂之庇軫參分弓長而揉其一參分其股</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='5460:5483'>　圍去一為蚤圍參分弓長以其一為之尊上欲尊而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='5483:5518'>　宇欲卑<span class='krp-note'>上近部則欲其髙隤下/為宇則欲其低卑音婢</span>上尊而宇卑則吐疾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='5518:5552'>　而霤逺<span class='krp-note'>其勢順霤/力又反</span>蓋已崇則難為門也<span class='krp-note'>髙則門/難容</span>蓋已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='5552:5585'>　卑是蔽目也<span class='krp-note'>卑則遮/前不見</span>是故蓋崇十尺<span class='krp-note'>髙十/尺</span>良蓋弗冐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='5585:5626'>　弗紘<span class='krp-note'>善為蓋者不以衣覆/或有衣而不以線係</span>殷畆而馳不隊<span class='krp-note'>隊讀謂墜/如平畆而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='5626:5652'>　<span class='krp-note'>馳且落不/落之狀</span>謂之國工<span class='krp-note'>是國之/良工也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='5652:5680'>輿人為車<span class='krp-note'>車謂/五路</span>輪崇車廣衡長參如一謂之參稱參分</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='5680:5707'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-10a' );" name="011-10a" class="pb">[011-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='5707:5730'>　車廣去一以為隧參分其隧一在前二在後以揉其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='5730:5753'>　式以其廣之半為之式崇以其隧之半為之較崇六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='5753:5776'>　分其廣以一為之軫圍參分軫圍去一以為式圍參</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='5776:5799'>　分式圍去一以為較圍參分較圍去一以為軹圍參</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='5799:5829'>　分軹圍去一以為轛圍圜者中規<span class='krp-note'>為圓必中於/規中去聲</span>方者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='5829:5872'>　中矩<span class='krp-note'>為方必/中於矩</span>立者中縣<span class='krp-note'>立者必如縣/繩之直縣𤣥</span>衡者中水<span class='krp-note'>衡者/必如</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='5872:5912'>　<span class='krp-note'>止水/之平</span>直者如生焉<span class='krp-note'>如木之/生於地</span>繼者如附焉<span class='krp-note'>如木之/附於榦</span>凡居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='5912:5948'>　材大與小無并<span class='krp-note'>處材得其所以小入大大/者受之而入無兼并之失</span>大倚小則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='5948:5975'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-10b' );" name="011-10b" class="pb">[011-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='5975:5991'>　摧引之則絶棧車欲弇飾車欲侈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='5991:6032'>輈人為輈<span class='krp-note'>輈車轅也/輈張留反</span>輈有三度<span class='krp-note'>淺深異/其數也</span>軸有三理<span class='krp-note'>言其/有常</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='6032:6071'>　<span class='krp-note'>也/</span>國馬之輈<span class='krp-note'>種馬駕玉路戎馬駕革路/齊馬駕金路道馬駕象路</span>深四尺有七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='6071:6114'>　寸<span class='krp-note'>國馬髙八尺故輈之深/四尺七寸深去聲下同</span>田馬之輈<span class='krp-note'>駕木/路</span>深四尺<span class='krp-note'>田/馬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='6114:6154'>　<span class='krp-note'>髙七尺故輈/之深四尺</span>駑馬之輈<span class='krp-note'>駕役/車</span>深三尺有三寸<span class='krp-note'>駑馬髙/六尺故</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='6154:6192'>　<span class='krp-note'>輈之深三尺三寸/此言輈有三度也</span>　軸有三理<span class='krp-note'>釋三理/之義</span>一者以為媺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='6192:6231'>　也<span class='krp-note'>軸之材欲其美/而無惡媺美同</span>二者以為乆也<span class='krp-note'>軸之體欲其/堅而可乆</span>三者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='6231:6266'>　以為利也<span class='krp-note'>軸之勢欲其利而易轉/  此言軸有三理也</span>軌前十尺而䇿半</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='6266:6293'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-11a' );" name="011-11a" class="pb">[011-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='6293:6316'>　之凡任木任正者十分其輈之長以其一為之圍衡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='6316:6339'>　任者五分其長以其一為之圍小於度謂之無任五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='6339:6362'>　分其軫間以其一為之軸圍十分其輈之長以其一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='6362:6385'>　為之當兔之圍參分其兔圍去一以為頸圍五分其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='6385:6408'>　頸圍去一以為踵圍凡揉輈欲其孫而無弧深今夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='6408:6431'>　大車之轅摯其登又難既克其登其覆車也必易此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='6431:6454'>　無故惟轅直且無橈也是故大車平地既節軒摯之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='6454:6477'>　任及其登阤不伏其轅必縊其牛此無故惟轅直且</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='6477:6504'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-11b' );" name="011-11b" class="pb">[011-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='6504:6527'>　無橈也故登阤者倍任者也猶能以登及其下阤也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='6527:6550'>　不援其邸必緧其牛後此無故惟轅直且無橈也是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='6550:6573'>　故輈欲頎典輈深則折淺則負輈注則利準利準則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='6573:6600'>　乆和則安輈欲弧而無折經而無絶進則與馬謀<span class='krp-note'>馬/所</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='6600:6640'>　<span class='krp-note'>以駕車故車之/進則與馬謀</span>退則與人謀<span class='krp-note'>人所以御馬故車/之退則與人謀</span>終日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='6640:6684'>　馳騁<span class='krp-note'>雖終日用之/以馳騁驅驟</span>左不揵<span class='krp-note'>車左君聴乗揵倦也言尊/者在左無揵倦之病也揵</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='6684:6726'>　<span class='krp-note'>蹇/</span>行數千里<span class='krp-note'>雖行數千/里之逺</span>馬不契需<span class='krp-note'>契傷也言馬不傷/於蹄不濡滯於路</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='6726:6769'>　<span class='krp-note'>也契苦/結反</span>終嵗御<span class='krp-note'>雖終嵗/御車</span>衣袵不敝<span class='krp-note'>袵裳際也車行無/動搖故不損御者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='6769:6796'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-12a' );" name="011-12a" class="pb">[011-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='6796:6833'>　<span class='krp-note'>之衣/裳也</span>此惟輈之和也<span class='krp-note'>凡此三者以輈/之和故能如此</span>勸登馬力馬力</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='6833:6856'>　既竭輈猶能一取焉良輈環灂自伏兔不至軌七寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='6856:6889'>　軌中有灂謂之國輈軫之方也<span class='krp-note'>軫輿後/横木也</span>以象地也<span class='krp-note'>軫/在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='6889:6933'>　<span class='krp-note'>下以承上也/故象地之方</span>蓋之圜也<span class='krp-note'>蓋周圍/覆車也</span>以象天也<span class='krp-note'>蓋在上以/覆下故以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='6933:6974'>　<span class='krp-note'>象天/之圜</span>輪輻三十<span class='krp-note'>一輪有/三十輻</span>以象日月也<span class='krp-note'>象一月有/三十日也</span>蓋弓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='6974:7010'>　二十有八<span class='krp-note'>一蓋有二/十八弓</span>以象星也<span class='krp-note'>象天有二/十八宿也</span>龍旂九斿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='7010:7052'>　<span class='krp-note'>交龍為旂其斿/有九諸侯建之</span>以象大火也<span class='krp-note'>大火蒼龍之宿東/方之星其屬有九</span>鳥旟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='7052:7094'>　七斿<span class='krp-note'>鳥準為旟其斿有/七州里建之旟余</span>以象鶉火也<span class='krp-note'>鶉火朱鳥之宿/南方之星其屬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='7094:7121'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-12b' );" name="011-12b" class="pb">[011-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='7121:7165'>　<span class='krp-note'>有七/鶉淳</span>熊旗六斿<span class='krp-note'>熊虎為旗其斿/有六師都建之</span>以象伐也<span class='krp-note'>伐白虎之/宿西方之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='7165:7209'>　<span class='krp-note'>星其屬/有六也</span>龜蛇四斿<span class='krp-note'>龜蛇為旐其斿/有四縣都建之</span>以象營室也<span class='krp-note'>營室/𤣥武</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='7209:7251'>　<span class='krp-note'>之宿北方之/星其屬有四</span>弧旌枉矢<span class='krp-note'>凡旌旗皆有弧以張/之又畫枉矢於上也</span>以象弧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='7251:7268'>　也<span class='krp-note'>以象弧星之/有矢飛行也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='7268:7309'>攻金之工<span class='krp-note'>此下言用金/錫多寡之法</span>築氏執下齊<span class='krp-note'>多錫為下齊築氏/為削則用錫為多</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='7309:7347'>　<span class='krp-note'>齊去聲/下同</span>冶氏執上齊<span class='krp-note'>少錫為上齊冶氏為/戈㦸則用錫為少</span>鳬氏為聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='7347:7386'>　<span class='krp-note'>鐘錞/之屬</span>㮚氏為量<span class='krp-note'>斗斛之屬/量去聲</span>段氏為鏄器<span class='krp-note'>錢鏄/之屬</span>桃氏為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='7386:7425'>　刄<span class='krp-note'>刃劍/之屬</span>金有六齊<span class='krp-note'>用錫和金/其齊有六</span>六分其金而錫居一<span class='krp-note'>金/五</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='7425:7452'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-13a' );" name="011-13a" class="pb">[011-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='7452:7492'>　<span class='krp-note'>分錫一分/共六分</span>謂之鍾鼎之齊<span class='krp-note'>鍾以擊鼎以烹比之/斧斤則用錫為差少</span>五分</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='7492:7528'>　其金而錫居一<span class='krp-note'>金四分錫一/分共五分</span>謂之斧斤之齊<span class='krp-note'>斧以伐/斤以削</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='7528:7566'>　<span class='krp-note'>比之鍾鼎則/用錫為差少</span>四分其金而錫居一<span class='krp-note'>金三分錫一/分共四分</span>謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='7566:7607'>　戈㦸之齊<span class='krp-note'>戈㦸皆用以擊刺防其挫折故比之斧/斤則用錫為多也以上三者皆上齊也</span>三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='7607:7642'>　分其金而錫居一<span class='krp-note'>金二分錫一/分共三分</span>謂之大刄之齊<span class='krp-note'>大刄/以施</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='7642:7683'>　<span class='krp-note'>之斬伐防其易虧比/之戈㦸則用錫尤多</span>五分其金而錫居二<span class='krp-note'>金三分錫/二分共五</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='7683:7724'>　<span class='krp-note'>分/</span>謂之削殺矢之齊<span class='krp-note'>削書刀也用以削書殺矢箭也/用以田獵皆欲其堅忍不脆比</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='7724:7767'>　<span class='krp-note'>之大刄則/用錫又多</span>金錫半<span class='krp-note'>金一半/錫一半</span>謂之鑒燧之齊<span class='krp-note'>鑒取水於/月燧取火</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='7767:7794'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-13b' );" name="011-13b" class="pb">[011-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='7794:7823'>　<span class='krp-note'>於日皆以潔白為上故金錫/半之  以上三者皆下齊也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='7823:7863'>築氏為削<span class='krp-note'>書刀也刋/竹簡用之</span>長尺博寸<span class='krp-note'>削之制/長與大</span>合六而成規<span class='krp-note'>其/形</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='7863:7904'>　<span class='krp-note'>容大/成規</span>欲新而無窮<span class='krp-note'>常欲其如新發之/於硎用之不窮</span>敝盡而無惡<span class='krp-note'>雖/至</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='7904:7917'>　<span class='krp-note'>敝終無頓/缺之患</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='7917:7940'>冶氏為殺矢刄長寸圍寸鋌十之重三垸戈廣二寸内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='7940:7963'>　倍之胡三之援四之已倨則不入已句則不決長内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='7963:7986'>　則折前短内則不疾是故倨句外愽重二鋝㦸廣寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='7986:8009'>　有半寸内三之胡四之援五之倨句中矩與刺重三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='8009:8036'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-14a' );" name="011-14a" class="pb">[011-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='8036:8040'>　鋝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='8040:8073'>桃氏為劒<span class='krp-note'>劒工謂之桃氏以/能辟除不祥故也</span>臘廣二寸有半寸兩從半</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='8073:8096'>　之以其臘廣為之莖圍長倍之中其莖設其後參分</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='8096:8124'>　其臘廣去一以為首廣而圍之身長五其莖長<span class='krp-note'>手所/握者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='8124:8170'>　<span class='krp-note'>謂之莖其長五寸劍身長五/倍於莖則共長三尺也臘納</span>重九鋝<span class='krp-note'>一鋝重六兩半/有零九鋝則重</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='8170:8211'>　<span class='krp-note'>六十兩/也鋝劣</span>謂之上制<span class='krp-note'>此劍之/上等</span>上士服之<span class='krp-note'>勇士之上/者能用之</span>身長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='8211:8251'>　四其莖長<span class='krp-note'>共長二/尺五寸</span>重七鋝<span class='krp-note'>重四十六/兩有餘</span>謂之中制<span class='krp-note'>此劍/之中</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='8251:8289'>　<span class='krp-note'>等/</span>中士服之<span class='krp-note'>勇士之中/者能用之</span>身長三其莖長<span class='krp-note'>共長/二尺</span>重五鋝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='8289:8316'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-14b' );" name="011-14b" class="pb">[011-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='8316:8355'>　<span class='krp-note'>重三十/兩有餘</span>謂之下制<span class='krp-note'>此劍之/下等</span>下士服之<span class='krp-note'>勇士之下/者能用之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='8355:8388'>鳬氏為鍾<span class='krp-note'>鳬入氷不溺以名鍾/工取其虚浮之義</span>兩灓謂之銑銑間謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='8388:8411'>　于于上謂之鼓鼔上謂之鉦鉦上謂之舞舞上謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='8411:8434'>　甬甬上謂之衡鍾縣謂之旋旋蟲謂之幹鍾帶謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='8434:8459'>　篆篆間謂之枚枚謂之景于上之攠謂之隧十分其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='8459:8482'>　銑去二以為鉦以其鉦為之銑間去二分以為之鼓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='8482:8509'>　間以其鼓間為之舞修去二分以為舞廣以其鉦<span class='krp-note'>音/正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='8509:8532'>　之長為之甬長以其甬長為之圍參分其圍去一以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='8532:8559'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-15a' );" name="011-15a" class="pb">[011-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='8559:8582'>　為衡圍參分其甬長二在上一在下以設其旋薄厚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='8582:8620'>　之所震動<span class='krp-note'>薄厚不得其宜/則震動不得中</span>清濁之所由出<span class='krp-note'>聲之清濁/出於此</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='8620:8658'>　侈弇之所由興<span class='krp-note'>口之侈弇/起於此</span>有説<span class='krp-note'>當推其弊之所/由出説始鋭反</span>鍾已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='8658:8698'>　厚則石<span class='krp-note'>其聲/不出</span>已薄則播<span class='krp-note'>聲/散</span>侈則柞<span class='krp-note'>形大則聲迫/窄柞側百反</span>弇則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='8698:8738'>　鬱<span class='krp-note'>形小則聲/鬱而不散</span>長甬則震<span class='krp-note'>甬鍾柄也甬長則/震而不定甬音勇</span>是故大鍾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='8738:8761'>　十分其鼓間以其一為之厚小鍾十分其鉦間以其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='8761:8792'>　一為之厚鍾大而短<span class='krp-note'>鍾形大則宜/長而失於短</span>則其聲疾而短聞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='8792:8832'>　<span class='krp-note'>疾急也短聞者/聲易竭也聞問</span>鍾小而長<span class='krp-note'>鍾形小則宜/短而失於長</span>則其聲舒而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='8832:8859'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-15b' );" name="011-15b" class="pb">[011-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='8859:8890'>　逺聞<span class='krp-note'>舒緩也逺聞/謂聲難息也</span>為遂六分其厚以其一為之深而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='8890:8895'>　圜之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='8895:8934'>㮚氏為量<span class='krp-note'>㮚與栗同以名量/工取其堅實之義</span>改煎金錫則不耗<span class='krp-note'>量則鍾/鼎之齊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='8934:8977'>　<span class='krp-note'>必煉之使精而無/減耗然後可用也</span>不耗然後權之<span class='krp-note'>權稱錘也權之所/以眡其輕重之齊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='8977:9014'>　<span class='krp-note'>也/</span>權之然後準之<span class='krp-note'>準取法於水也準之所/以眡其髙下之平也</span>準之然後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='9014:9054'>　量之<span class='krp-note'>量之以黍所以眡/其多寡之均也</span>量之以為鬴<span class='krp-note'>一鬴容六斗/四升鬴音父</span>深</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='9054:9091'>　尺<span class='krp-note'>其深/一尺</span>内方尺而圜其外<span class='krp-note'>内方一尺而外圜/象天包地外也</span>其實鬴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='9091:9132'>　<span class='krp-note'>四豆為區/四區為鬴</span>其臋一寸<span class='krp-note'>臋厚一/寸臋豚</span>其實一豆<span class='krp-note'>四升/為豆</span>其耳三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='9132:9159'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-16a' );" name="011-16a" class="pb">[011-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='9159:9199'>　寸<span class='krp-note'>耳廣/三寸</span>其實一升<span class='krp-note'>四龠為合/四合為升</span>重一鈞<span class='krp-note'>重三/十斤</span>其聲中黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='9199:9240'>　鍾之宫<span class='krp-note'>黄鍾律長九寸上下損益生十二律五聲/之中宫聲為君量之聲應之也中去聲</span>槩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='9240:9283'>　而不税<span class='krp-note'>用槩所以為平也不/征其税所以為公也</span>其銘曰<span class='krp-note'>刻於量上以銘/之其辭如下文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='9283:9326'>　<span class='krp-note'>所/云</span>時文思索<span class='krp-note'>時是也惟是文徳之/君思索以求其理</span>允臻其極<span class='krp-note'>允信也/極中也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='9326:9371'>　<span class='krp-note'>作為比量使天下/取信而至於中也</span>嘉量既成<span class='krp-note'>量成而名之曰嘉所以/一天下之法而極其美</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='9371:9413'>　<span class='krp-note'>也/</span>以觀四國<span class='krp-note'>其法度之器可以觀示/四方之國也觀音貫</span>永啓厥後<span class='krp-note'>永乆/開啓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='9413:9449'>　<span class='krp-note'>其後世/子孫</span>茲器維則<span class='krp-note'>使後世惟以此/器為法則也</span>凡鑄金之狀金與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='9449:9472'>　錫黒濁之氣竭黄白次之黄白之氣竭青白次之青</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='9472:9499'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-16b' );" name="011-16b" class="pb">[011-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='9499:9515'>　白之氣竭青氣次之然後可鑄也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='9515:9523'>段氏<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='9523:9564'>函人為甲<span class='krp-note'>包函不至傷/人掌為甲</span>犀甲七屬<span class='krp-note'>以犀皮次叙聨屬其/甲屬謂上旅下旅相</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='9564:9606'>　<span class='krp-note'>績之數/屬音注</span>兕甲六屬<span class='krp-note'>以兕牛/皮貫甲</span>合甲五屬<span class='krp-note'>合犀兕之革/貫甲尤堅</span>犀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='9606:9635'>　甲夀百年兕甲夀二百年合甲夀三百年<span class='krp-note'>革堅者/用愈乆</span>凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='9635:9663'>　為甲必先為容<span class='krp-note'>容象/式也</span>然後制革權其上旅與其下旅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='9663:9686'>　而重若一以其長為之圍凡甲鍛不摯則不堅已敝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='9686:9709'>　則橈凡察革之道眡其鑚空欲其惌也眡其裏欲其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='9709:9736'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-17a' );" name="011-17a" class="pb">[011-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='9736:9766'>　易也眡其朕欲其直也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1060' title='KR1060' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1060.png'/>之欲其約也舉而眡之欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='9766:9789'>　其豐也衣之欲其無齘也眡其鑚空而惌則革堅也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='9789:9819'>　眡其裏而易則材更也眡其朕而直則制善也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1060' title='KR1060' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1060.png'/>之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='9819:9841'>　而約則周也舉之而豐則明也衣之無齘則變也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='9841:9864'>鮑人之事望而眡之欲其荼白也進而握之欲其柔而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='9864:9887'>　滑也卷而搏之欲其無迆也眡其著欲其淺也察其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='9887:9910'>　線欲其藏也革欲其荼白而疾澣之則堅欲其柔滑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='9910:9933'>　而腛脂之則需引而信之欲其直也信之而直則取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='9933:9960'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-17b' );" name="011-17b" class="pb">[011-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='9960:9983'>　材正也信之而枉則是一方緩一方急也若苟一方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='9983:10006'>　緩一方急則及其用之也必自其急者先裂若苟自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='10006:10029'>　急者先裂則是以愽為帴也卷而博之而不迆則厚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='10029:10052'>　薄序也眡其著而淺則革信也察其線而藏則雖敝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='10052:10057'>　不甐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='10057:10092'>韗人為皋陶<span class='krp-note'>韗人為鼔皋陶以木為/之鼔之匡也韗運陶逃</span>長六尺有六寸左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='10092:10115'>　右端廣六寸中尺厚三寸穹者二之一上三正鼓長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='10115:10138'>　八尺鼓四尺中圍加三之一謂之鼖鼔為皋鼓長尋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='10138:10165'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-18a' );" name="011-18a" class="pb">[011-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='10165:10192'>　有四尺鼓四尺倨句磬折凡冐鼓必以啓蟄之曰<span class='krp-note'>驚/蟄</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='10192:10232'>　<span class='krp-note'>日冐鼔/冐象也</span>良鼓瑕如積環<span class='krp-note'>其用革之調急隨皋/陶之周圍若環之圓</span>鼓大而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='10232:10259'>　短則其聲疾而短聞鼓小而長則其聲舒而逺聞<span class='krp-note'>義/與</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='10259:10273'>　<span class='krp-note'>鳬氏為鍾/同聞音問</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='10273:10281'>韋氏<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='10281:10289'>裘氏<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='10289:10322'>畫繢之事<span class='krp-note'>模成物體謂之畫/分布五色謂之繢</span>雜五色東方謂之青南方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='10322:10346'>　謂之赤西方謂之白北方謂之黒天謂之𤣥地謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='10346:10373'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-18b' );" name="011-18b" class="pb">[011-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='10373:10397'>　黄青與白相次也赤與黒相次也𤣥與黄相次也赤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='10397:10434'>　與青謂之文<span class='krp-note'>東方青色與南方赤/色相雜名之曰文</span>赤與白謂之章<span class='krp-note'>南/方</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='10434:10476'>　<span class='krp-note'>赤色與西方白色/相雜名之曰章</span>白與黒謂之黼<span class='krp-note'>黼為斧形取其斷/以西方白色與北</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='10476:10519'>　<span class='krp-note'>方黒色相雜/為之黼音甫</span>黒與青謂之黻<span class='krp-note'>黻為兩已相背取其辨/也以北方黒色與東方</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='10519:10558'>　<span class='krp-note'>青色相雜/為之黻紱</span>五采備謂之繡<span class='krp-note'>繡刺繡也備青/黄赤白黒之色</span>土以黄其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='10558:10581'>　象方天時變火以圜山以章水以龍鳥獸虵雜四時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='10581:10609'>　五色之位以章之謂之巧凡畫繢之事後素功<span class='krp-note'>謂後/於素</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='10609:10651'>　<span class='krp-note'>功也蓋先以粉地為質而後可施以五采也記/曰甘受和白受采孔子曰繪事後素此之謂也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='10651:10678'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-19a' );" name="011-19a" class="pb">[011-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='10678:10721'>鍾氏<span class='krp-note'>鍾重也染/色欲深重</span>染羽<span class='krp-note'>羽所以飾旌旗/及王后之車</span>以朱湛丹秫<span class='krp-note'>湛漬/漸也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='10721:10761'>　<span class='krp-note'>丹秫赤栗也取汁/染明湛子潜反</span>三月而熾之<span class='krp-note'>熾炊/也</span>淳而漬之<span class='krp-note'>漬染/也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='10761:10795'>　三入為纁五入為緅七入為緇<span class='krp-note'>三染為纁謂染朱黒/色五染赤汁及黒色</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='10795:10815'>　<span class='krp-note'>為緅七入染汁為/黒白緇緅側留反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='10815:10823'>筐人<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='10823:10864'>㡛氏<span class='krp-note'>治絲帛而練熟/之為㡛㡛音芒</span>湅絲以涗水<span class='krp-note'>涗水灰水也涷/音練涗書銳反</span>漚其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='10864:10898'>　絲七日<span class='krp-note'>漚鳥豆/反漸也</span>去地尺暴之<span class='krp-note'>暴步/卜反</span>晝暴諸日夜宿諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='10898:10927'>　井七日七夜是謂水湅<span class='krp-note'>此涷絲/之法度</span>湅白以欄為灰渥淳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='10927:10954'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '011-19b' );" name="011-19b" class="pb">[011-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='10954:10977'>　其帛實諸澤器淫之以蜃清其灰而盝之而揮之而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='10977:11000'>　沃之而盝之而塗之而宿之明日沃而盝之晝暴諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='11000:11016'>　日夜宿諸井七日七夜是謂水涷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='11016:11019'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='11019:11022'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='11022:11025'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='11025:11028'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='11028:11038'>　周禮句解卷十一</span><br/>
</p>
